episodes.title: What Jehovah's Witnesses Actually Believe
episodes.description:
This cartoon is from Leonard Chretien's film "Witnesses of Jehovah" that accompanied the 1988 book of the same name. Yes, this is pretty much exactly what Jehovah's Witnesses believe, as stupid as it sounds.
